Assignment-2:
-------------------------
#Find sum of digits in given number.
n=int(input('Enter a number: '))
sum=0
while n>0 :
   rem=n%10
   if rem!=0 :
      sum=sum+rem
   n=n//10
print('The sum of digits in entered number is: ',sum)
O/p:
-------
Enter a number: 9999
The sum of digits in entered number is:  36

